name: Saci on Paper
description:
This is the Saci arrangement's score.

Five other musicians and I spent weeks studying this score until we were able to record Saci.

This is about musical process!


Davi Fonseca – Composition, arrangement, piano, keyboard, especial piano and voice. 
Alexandre Andrés – C flute
Alexandre Silva – Bass clarinet
Camila Rocha – Acustic bass
Natália Mitre – Vibraphone e Marimba
Yuri Vellasco – Drums and Percussion

Pedro Durães - musical production
